sellerCard.oneLiner: Full Stack Software, Mobile Application, Website and Web App Developer
sellerCard.description: Hi! I am Junaid and I am an experienced Frontend & Backend Developer with expertise in JavaScript, PHP, HTML5, CSS3, MySQL, MongoDB, and PHP. I have done many projects using various frameworks like ReactJs, Next JS, React Native, Node JS, Laravel, and core PHP. I can build websites and desktop applications in the above frameworks and can fix any bugs regarding these technologies. Your work will be done with full strength and satisfaction. My friendly service is waiting for you to order.

description.content:
Hi

I am a professional fullstack website developer and designer working for the past 5+ years I have built many custom websites for different customers and fixed bugs for their business projects. I have also rebuilt many projects for my clients in advanced technology. Please feel free to contact me for any kind of project whether it is basic or complex. I am also experienced with MySQL databases.


My areas of expertise include:


  • Database
  • Custom Website Design and Development
  • PHP
  • React js
  • WordPress development
  • BigCommerce
  • Wix
  • MySQL
  • HTML5
  • CSS3
  • jQuery
  • Javascript
  • Google AMP




Tools I Use:


  • Visual Code
  • PHP Storm
  • Wamp Server
  • Xampp Server



I am committed to creating attractive, high-performing websites using the latest technologies. Whether you need a new website or have a custom project in mind, I am here to help.


NOTE: Message me first before placing the order.
